channel.title: Teleports
channel.description:
You know how the emote tabs are sometimes teleports to places in your private server. How do i change the coordinates on the tabs to make them go to different places?
Please help.

item.title: Teleports
item.dc:creator: @memorial memorial
item.description:
@memorial wrote:

well, the emote tabs have to do with a command and you set the tab to use that command so.

If the tab says “home” search for the command home and change the coords and so forth.

open up client.java

search for customCommand("home")

this means that it is saying that the tab that says “Home” will use the custom command “home”

so go to the home teleport command and change the coords

hope i could help! =P

if anymore questions add my msn guthixfreak93@hotmail.com
